INSERT INTO `creature_text` (`entry`,`groupid`,`id`,`text`,`type`,`language`,`probability`,`emote`,`duration`,`sound`,`comment`) VALUES
(37119,0,0, 'This is our final stand. What happens here will echo through the ages. Regardless of outcome, they will know that we fought with honor. That we fought for the freedom and safety of our people!',1,0,100,22,0,0, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring'),
(37119,0,0, 'Remember, heroes, fear is your greatest enemy in these befouled halls. Steel your heart and your soul will shine brighter than a thousand suns. The enemy will falter at the sight of you. They will fall as the light of righteousness envelops them!',1,0,100,22,0,0, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring'),
(37119,0,0, 'Our march upon Icecrown Citadel begins now!',1,0,100,22,0,0, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring'),
(37181,0,0, 'You now stand upon the hallowed ground of the Scourge. The Light won''t protect you here, paladin. Nothing will protect you...',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'The Lich King'),
(37119,0,0, 'ARTHAS! I swore that I would see you dead and the Scourge dismantled! I''m going to finish what I started at Light''s Hope!',1,0,100,22,0,0, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring'),
(37181,0,0, 'You could have been my greatest champion, Fordring: A force of darkness that would wash over this world and deliver it into a new age of strife.',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'The Lich King'),
(37181,0,0, 'But that honor is no longer yours. Soon, I will have a new champion.',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'The Lich King'),
(37181,0,0, 'The breaking of this one has been taxing. The atrocities I have committed upon his soul. He has resisted for so long, but he will bow down before his king soon.',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'The Lich King'),
(37183,0,0, 'NEVER! I... I will never... serve... you...',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Highlord Bolvar Fordragon'),
(37181,0,0, 'In the end, you will all serve me.',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'The Lich King'),
(37200,0,0, 'Could it be, Lord Fordring? If Bolvar lives, mayhap there is hope fer peace between the Alliance and the Horde. We must reach the top o'' this cursed place and free the paladin!',0,0,100,0,0,0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard'),
(37119,0,0, 'By the Light, it must be so!',0,0,100,5,0,0, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring'),
(37200,0,0, 'Prepare the Skybreaker fer an aerial assault on the citadel!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard'),
(37200,0,0, 'Heroes, ye must fight yer way to a clear extraction point within Icecrown. We''ll try an'' rendezvous on the ramparts!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard'),
(37007,0,0, 'Who... goes there...?',1,0,100,5,0,0, 'Deathbound Ward'),
(36612,0,0, 'This is the beginning AND the end, mortals. None may enter the master''s sanctum!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lord Marrowgar'),
(36612,0,0, 'The Scourge will wash over this world as a swarm of death and destruction!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lord Marrowgar'),
(36612,0,0, 'More bones for the offering!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lord Marrowgar'),
(36612,0,0, 'The only escape is death!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lord Marrowgar'),
(36612,0,0, '%s creates a whirling storm of bone!',3,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lord Marrowgar'),
(36612,0,0, 'BONE STORM!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lord Marrowgar'),
(36612,0,0, 'Languish in damnation!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lord Marrowgar'),
(36612,0,0, 'Bound by bone!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lord Marrowgar'),
(36612,0,0, 'Stick around!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lord Marrowgar'),
(36612,0,0, 'I see... Only darkness.',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lord Marrowgar'),
(36855,0,0, 'You have found your way here, because you are among the few gifted with true vision in a world cursed with blindness.',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lady Deathwhisper'),
(36855,0,0, 'You can see through the fog that hangs over this world like a shroud, and grasp where true power lies.',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lady Deathwhisper'),
(36855,0,0, 'Fix your eyes upon your crude hands: the sinew, the soft meat, the dark blood coursing within.',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lady Deathwhisper'),
(36855,0,0, 'It is a weakness; a crippling flaw....  A joke played by the Creators upon their own creations.',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lady Deathwhisper'),
(36855,0,0, 'The sooner you come to accept your condition as a defect, the sooner you will find yourselves in a position to transcend it.',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lady Deathwhisper'),
(36855,0,0, 'Through our Master, all things are possible. His power is without limit, and his will unbending.',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lady Deathwhisper'),
(36855,0,0, 'Those who oppose him will be destroyed utterly, and those who serve -- who serve wholly, unquestioningly, with utter devotion of mind and soul -- elevated to heights beyond your ken.',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lady Deathwhisper'),
(36855,0,0, 'What is this disturbance? You dare trespass upon this hallowed ground? This shall be your final resting place!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lady Deathwhisper'),
(38485,0,0, 'Die, intruders! None shall interfere with the Cult''s plans!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Darnavan'),
(36855,0,0, 'Take this blessing and show these intruders a taste of the Master''s power!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lady Deathwhisper'),
(36855,0,0, 'You are weak, powerless to resist my will!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lady Deathwhisper'),
(36855,0,0, 'Arise, and exult in your pure form!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lady Deathwhisper'),
(36855,0,0, 'Embrace the darkness... darkness eternal.',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lady Deathwhisper'),
(37007,0,0, 'The master''s sanctum has been disturbed!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Deathbound Ward'),
(36855,0,0, 'I release you from the curse of flesh!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lady Deathwhisper'),
(36855,0,0, '%s''s Mana Barrier shimmers and fades away!',3,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lady Deathwhisper'),
(36855,0,0, 'Enough! I see I must take matters into my own hands!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lady Deathwhisper'),
(36855,0,0, 'Do you yet grasp the futility of your actions?',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lady Deathwhisper'),
(36855,0,0, 'All part of the Master''s plan.... Your end is inevitable....',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Lady Deathwhisper'),
(37003,0,0, 'Thank goodness you arrived when you did, heroes. Orgrim''s Hammer has already left. Quickly now, to the Skybreaker! If you leave soon, you may be able to catch them.',0,0,100,0,0,17154, 'Skybreaker Vindicator'),
(36998,0,0, 'You have my thanks. We were outnumbered until you arrived.',0,0,100,1,0,17157, 'Skybreaker Protector'),
(36998,0,0, 'Captain Muradin is waiting aboard the Skybreaker. We''ll secure the area until you are ready for take off.',0,0,100,397,0,0, 'Skybreaker Protector'),
(37230,0,0, 'A screeching cry pierces the air above!',3,0,100,0,0,0, 'Spire Frostwyrm'),
(36948,0,0, 'Fire up the engines! We got a meetin'' with destiny, lads!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard'),
(36948,0,0, 'Hold on to yer hats!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard'),
(36948,0,0, 'What in the world is that? Grab me spyglass, crewman!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard'),
(36948,0,0, 'By me own beard! HORDE SAILIN'' IN FAST ''N HOT!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard'),
(36948,0,0, 'EVASIVE ACTION! MAN THE GUNS!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard'),
(36948,0,0, 'Cowardly dogs! Ye blindsided us!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard'),
(36939,0,0, 'This is not your battle, dwarf. Back down or we will be forced to destroy your ship.',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'High Overlord Saurfang'),
(36948,0,0, 'Not me battle? I dunnae who ye think ye are, mister, but I got a score to settle with Arthas and yer not gettin'' in me way! FIRE ALL GUNS! FIRE! FIRE!',1,0,100,0,0,0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard'),
